Get To Know Better

Technology can serve as a foundation for quality businesses on your journey towards excellence. Where many software companies focus on growth, our team puts a preference for quality and ensuring every little detail is the best it can be, because our partners deserve nothing less.

Our Leadership

The company has progressed in leaps and bounds under the stewardship of our inspiring Director Mr. Mahesh Viswam. Mahesh brings to the table a wealth of experience of over 25 years in the Information Technology field, nearly 18 of which were spent in GCC. Prior to coming on board Mobatia in 2014, he handled leadership roles in UAE where he was responsible for building, developing and leading IT teams for the government and the private sector.

Our vision

Our Vision is to be the most sought-after IT service provider. The Mobatia philosophy of service delivery is that we do not rest until our client recognizes the value of our services, which is always about running the extra mile.
